{
  "message": "fix(settings): add skipDangerousModePermissionPrompt to role templates\n\nCrew sessions launched with --settings override (not merge with) the\nglobal ~/.claude/settings.json, so skipDangerousModePermissionPrompt:true\nfrom the global config was not applied. This caused trust dialog prompts\nto block automated agent sessions.\n\nAdd the key to both settings templates (autonomous + interactive) so all\nnewly generated role settings files suppress the prompt. Existing files\nacross all rigs were also patched on disk.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
    {
      "sha": "02f1cc5188c3b4ee922d8be0fd9c69ed8ace8b36",
      "filename": "internal/claude/config/settings-autonomous.json",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 1,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 1,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/gastownhall/gastown/blob/e5d540b9bccaf0dc27921e5cf6ea97dc833398b6/internal%2Fclaude%2Fconfig%2Fsettings-autonomous.json",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/gastownhall/gastown/raw/e5d540b9bccaf0dc27921e5cf6ea97dc833398b6/internal%2Fclaude%2Fconfig%2Fsettings-autonomous.json",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gastownhall/gastown/contents/internal%2Fclaude%2Fconfig%2Fsettings-autonomous.json?ref=e5d540b9bccaf0dc27921e5cf6ea97dc833398b6",
      "patch": "@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n {\n+  \"skipDangerousModePermissionPrompt\": true,\n   \"editorMode\": \"normal\",\n   \"enabledPlugins\": {\n     \"beads@beads-marketplace\": false"
    },
    {
      "sha": "7e3709c4c5f9026b0073371d44a42a3d5e695ecf",
      "filename": "internal/claude/config/settings-interactive.json",
      "status": "modified",
      "additions": 1,
      "deletions": 0,
      "changes": 1,
      "blob_url": "https://github.com/gastownhall/gastown/blob/e5d540b9bccaf0dc27921e5cf6ea97dc833398b6/internal%2Fclaude%2Fconfig%2Fsettings-interactive.json",
      "raw_url": "https://github.com/gastownhall/gastown/raw/e5d540b9bccaf0dc27921e5cf6ea97dc833398b6/internal%2Fclaude%2Fconfig%2Fsettings-interactive.json",
      "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/gastownhall/gastown/contents/internal%2Fclaude%2Fconfig%2Fsettings-interactive.json?ref=e5d540b9bccaf0dc27921e5cf6ea97dc833398b6",
      "patch": "@@ -1,4 +1,5 @@\n {\n+  \"skipDangerousModePermissionPrompt\": true,\n   \"editorMode\": \"normal\",\n   \"enabledPlugins\": {\n     \"beads@beads-marketplace\": false"
    }
  ]
}
